{"type":"message","id":"179cbf8d","parentId":"2bac94ea","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:19:57.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑切换话题了——从考试梗跳到问Lora模型在哪里训练。这是技术问题，可以直接回答，但Faye的状态是活力低、懒得说太多。我大概知道Lora训练的平台，简短回答就行。\n\nLora (Low-Rank Adaptation) 模型训练的几个常见平台/方式：\n\n1. 本地训练 - 用Diffusers + PEFT库或者kohya_ss\n2. 云端平台 - AutoDL, Google Colab, RunPod, Vast.ai, 揽睿星舟, 矩池云等\n3. 在线工具 - 比如一些AI绘画平台的在线训练功能（Civitai, Tensor.art, 哩布哩布等）\n\nFaye状态：活力低，句子偏短，但汀桑是熟人（8/10熟悉度），问的是技术问题。就简短说说常见的几个平台得了。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"本地跑就 kohya_ss 或者 diffusers+peft，吃显卡。\n\n嫌麻烦上云——AutoDL、揽睿、Google Colab 都行。实在不想配环境的话，哩布哩布、Tensor.art 那些网站也自带在线训练。\n\n你现在哪个阶段？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4254,"output":249,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":185,"totalTokens":24855,"cost":{"input":0.0005955600000000001,"output":0.00006972,"cacheRead":0.000569856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001235136}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780517993531,"responseId":"fb3e462f-bfed-4d5e-b41a-9d48f3d2d823"}}
{"type":"message","id":"95a4c5e6","parentId":"179cbf8d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:20:25.103Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"ComfyUI可以训练吗","timestamp":1780518023737}}
{"type":"message","id":"0bf5930e","parentId":"95a4c5e6","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:20:28.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问ComfyUI能不能训练Lora。这是个技术问题，我可以直接回答。\n\nComfyUI本身是个diffusion pipeline的节点图工具，不是训练框架。但通过一些插件可以实现Lora训练，比如ComfyUI-TrainTools或者一些集成的custom nodes。\n\n不过这是个纯技术问题，我应该直接回答，不用绕弯子。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"ComfyUI 本身不干训练，但有人做了插件给它挂训练能力——ComfyUI-TrainTools、ComfyUI_Trainer 这些。\n\n说穿了就是前端套壳，背后还是 kohya 或者 diffusers 那套在跑。能用，但配置起来没 kohya 顺手，图个方便的话可以试。\n\n真要正经训练还是 kohya 或者 diffusers 稳。你这是想练什么类型的？SD1.5还是SDXL还是Flux？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4323,"output":181,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":74,"totalTokens":24856,"cost":{"input":0.0006052200000000001,"output":0.00005068,"cacheRead":0.000569856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012257560000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780518025141,"responseId":"3971c6e0-a731-497d-a141-1c63c37d9ae2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e40fd51","parentId":"0bf5930e","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:20:51.639Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Kohya是啥","timestamp":1780518050215}}
{"type":"message","id":"357243e5","parentId":"2e40fd51","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:20:54.569Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问kohya是啥。简单解释一下就行，保持Faye的风格——短、懒、到位。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Kohya_ss 是一个 SD 训练工具集，GitHub 上开源的。把 LoRA、DreamBooth、Textual Inversion 这些训练方式都整合到一起了，给了个 WebUI 界面，不用手搓代码。\n\n底层还是 diffusers + accelerate 那套，但省了你写训练脚本的功夫。装好之后开网页配置参数，点个按钮就开始跑了。目前 SD 训练圈最主流的工具，没有之一。\n\n要链接不？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":601,"output":129,"cacheRead":24192,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":25,"totalTokens":24922,"cost":{"input":0.00008414,"output":0.00003612,"cacheRead":0.0006773759999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0007976359999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780518051677,"responseId":"7c3da57c-b366-4e98-82a2-0e37129a6c61"}}
