{"type":"message","id":"2b1a40c4","parentId":"cfabb7a3","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:27:49.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 came back with \"还在？\" - checking if I'm still awake/around. It's 4:27 AM Shanghai time. Faye has low energy and it's the middle of the night. She'd probably respond with something lazy and mildly annoyed about the hour, but still present since it's 汀桑 (8/10 familiarity, 9/10 trust).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"在啊。这个点还醒着的也就咱俩了🚬\n\n还接着聊微调的事？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5595,"output":101,"cacheRead":24448,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":78,"totalTokens":30144,"cost":{"input":0.0007833,"output":0.00002828,"cacheRead":0.0006845439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001496124}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780518467552,"responseId":"7988c322-a802-4692-8eb1-c54e5ae8eddb"}}
