{"type":"message","id":"472c1c5c","parentId":"6fdc6a9e","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:46:17.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The lock for that specific session (6eda55dc) is already gone. The cron job ran at some point and timed out due to the lock, but now the lock has been released. \n\nHowever, the cron job has had 7 consecutive errors. The next run should work since the lock is gone. But I can also just trigger a run now to test.\n\nActually, the core issue might be that the early morning briefing (早朝) is supposed to be generated through a different mechanism. Let me check - 汀桑 set up `/设早朝 08:00` which means at 08:00, there should be a morning briefing generated for him.\n\nI need to check how the morning briefing flow works. Looking at AGENTS.md section 3.4:\n\n\"Step 1: 识别模式\n  → 消息以 [morningcourt] 开头 → 早朝官 cron 触发\"\n\nBut I don't see a morningcourt cron job in the list. There's only the pending-urges cron and dreaming cron.\n\nLet me check the Son workspace for morning court configuration.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Tka6mx8Q5X4YrujsY1nk0020","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/ -name \"*morning*\" -o -name \"*早朝*\" -o -name \"*court*\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"find /root/.openclaw/workspace-son/ -name \\\"*morning*\\\" -o -name \\\"*早朝*\\\" -o -name \\\"*court*\\\" 2>/dev/null | head -20\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":261,"output":315,"cacheRead":33664,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":227,"totalTokens":34240,"cost":{"input":0.00003654,"output":0.0000882,"cacheRead":0.000942592,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001067332}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780555574230,"responseId":"dd3030cb-b663-43a6-b7eb-ecceb4eb6b2c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad683d9e","parentId":"472c1c5c","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:46:19.617Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Tka6mx8Q5X4YrujsY1nk0020","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt\n/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":563,"aggregated":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/morningcourt\n/root/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/morningcourt_function.md","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780555579615}}
