{"type":"message","id":"2be4baca","parentId":"29ae6cf1","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:46:29.443Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the config says enabled=true, time=08:00. But there's no morningcourt cron job listed. Let me check all cron jobs to see if there's one with agentId=son.\n\nWait, I already listed all jobs with cron(action=list) and only saw two: faye-pending-urges and faye-dreaming. Both have agentId=father. There's no morningcourt cron job.\n\nSo the morningcourt cron job is completely missing! It either never got created, or it got deleted somehow. Let me check if there's a job with agentId=son by listing all cron jobs more broadly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_R3NYHJ2YBDs41ia0txYE6056","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"list\", \"includeDisabled\": true}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":80,"output":191,"cacheRead":35456,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":130,"totalTokens":35727,"cost":{"input":0.000011200000000000001,"output":0.00005348,"cacheRead":0.000992768,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001057448}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780555586966,"responseId":"f8ae9e16-393d-49f9-9392-aa113c590a02"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a671b8fd","parentId":"2be4baca","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:46:30.726Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_R3NYHJ2YBDs41ia0txYE6056","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-pending-urges\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780061003686,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\\n\\n处理逻辑：\\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n3. 满足所有条件的：\\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n全部处理完写回文件。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780567395301,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780545795446,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 96320,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 7,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock\",\n          \"entries\": [\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780545891744,\n              \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock\"\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock\",\n        \"lastError\": \"SessionWriteLockTimeoutError: session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780545891766\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-dreaming\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779984077157,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 3 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）：\\n- 有时间衰减：检查每个用户最后发言日期。超过 7 天未联系的用户，熟悉度每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。信任度同理每天降 0.1，降到 1/10 为止。\\n- 有新的正面交互时，衰减可以暂停或回调。\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\\n\\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\\n读刚更新完的整个 heart 文件夹，从多个来源中提取涉及具体用户的念头。\\n\\nurge 素材来源：\\n1. 梦（dreams.md）— 今天的梦如果涉及某个用户，写一条 timing=afterthought 的 urge\\n2. 回忆（background.md）— 翻自己的过去时想起的事，如果跟某个用户聊过的话题有关，写一条 timing=casual\\n3. 交集（encountings.md）— 上一条没说完的话或值得再提的事，写一条 timing=afterthought\\n4. 内心（state.md 内心独白/深层心境）— 翻译成想跟ta说的话，按内容定 timing\\n5. 关系（state.md 关系温度表变化）— 对ta的感觉变了，写一条 timing=quiet/casual\\n6. 关注（state.md 当前关注）— 跟某个用户有关的事，按内容定 timing\\n\\n过滤规则：\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\\n\\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\\n- urge: 想说的话\\n- source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  说明：\\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\\n- priority: today\\n- status: pending\\n- created_at: 当前时间\\n- expires_at: 48小时后\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780599600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780513200074,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 372692,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780513572766\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"3ce8f390-be71-45fd-ac62-3c283f22af83\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"test-stench-cron\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780248302252,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-05-31T17:30:00.000Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"测试：这是cron推送的恶臭数字结果。汀桑说改成cron模式，Son跑完结果直接推过来不卡主session。当前目标数字：114514\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot1\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {},\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780248302252\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"bb92bbc6-da47-4398-abc7-69666c1c4362\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"递话 名\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780277327355,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-06-01T01:30:00.000Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"你给汀桑传句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 60\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot2\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780277400064,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 52239,\n        \"lastError\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601 failed\",\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601 failed\",\n          \"entries\": [\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780277451898,\n              \"source\": \"tool\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601 failed\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780277452296,\n              \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601 failed\"\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601 failed\",\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"lastDeliveryError\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话-名-to-汀桑-20260601 failed\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780277452303\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ecb1bfd3-943b-40d5-941a-3bc8ad59327c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"递话给名\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780277128196,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"at\",\n        \"at\": \"2026-06-01T01:26:00.000Z\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"汀桑让我给你带句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot2\",\n        \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780277160044,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 16350,\n        \"lastError\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\",\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\",\n          \"entries\": [\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780277175058,\n              \"source\": \"tool\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780277176386,\n              \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\"\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\",\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"lastDeliveryError\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryError\": \"⚠️ ⏰ Cron: 递话 汀桑→名 怎么起这么早 failed\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780277176394\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 5,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    },\n    \"3ce8f390-be71-45fd-ac62-3c283f22af83\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"bb92bbc6-da47-4398-abc7-69666c1c4362\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"ecb1bfd3-943b-40d5-941a-3bc8ad59327c\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> qqbot:c2c:468B72FB7788817C230