一天内已给同一用户发过的不重复写文件\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件 pending_urges.md。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780567395301,"lastRunAtMs":1780545795446,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":96320,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":7,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock","entries":[{"ts":1780545891744,"source":"agent-run","severity":"error","message":"session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock","lastError":"SessionWriteLockTimeoutError: session file locked (timeout 60000ms): pid=17606 /root/.openclaw/agents/father/sessions/6eda55dc-6d70-43df-b019-e5067b5fb047.jsonl.lock","lastErrorReason":"timeout"},"updatedAtMs":1780555922096},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780555922797}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b5f11cb","parentId":"57231c0d","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:52:09.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, pending-urges cron updated. Now I need to create the outbox-sender cron. This cron will:\n- Run every 5 minutes (or maybe 10-15 to avoid being too frequent)\n- Read /tmp/faye-outbox/*.json files\n- For each file, create a one-shot announce cron with a minimal prompt that outputs only the message\n- Delete the file after processing\n\nActually, wait. I need to think about the delivery. The outbox-sender cron itself is an isolated agentTurn for father with delivery.mode=none. It will read files and create announce crons.\n\nThe announce cron it creates should have:\n- payload.kind = agentTurn (or can we use systemEvent? No, systemEvent goes to main session)\n- delivery.mode = announce with the specific user target\n\nBut the announce cron will still run an agent... which could leak work logs again.\n\nThe key fix here is: the announce cron's prompt should be **ultra minimal**. Something like:\n\n```\n请将以下消息原样输出，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要思考过程：\n\n{消息内容}\n```\n\nOr even simpler:\n\n```\n输出：{消息内容}\n```\n\nLet me create the outbox-sender cron now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_E910vLuJkHRnfLIuvEa82267","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"agentId":"father","name":"faye-outbox-sender","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"*/15 * * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"none"},"enabled":true,"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\n\n对每个文件，执行：\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\n   - agentId: father\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\n   - schedule: {kind: \"at\", at: \"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\"}\n   - payload: {kind: \"agentTurn\", message: \"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\n\\n{message}\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\n   - delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"{channel}\", accountId: \"{accountId}\", to: \"{to}\"}\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\n\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。","timeoutSeconds":60}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"add\", \"job\": {\"agentId\":\"father\",\"name\":\"faye-outbox-sender\",\"schedule\":{\"kind\":\"cron\",\"expr\":\"*/15 * * * *\",\"tz\":\"Asia/Shanghai\"},\"sessionTarget\":\"isolated\",\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"none\"},\"enabled\":true,\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\\n\\n对每个文件，执行：\\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\\n   - agentId: father\\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\\n   - schedule: {kind: \\\"at\\\", at: \\\"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\\\"}\\n   - payload: {kind: \\\"agentTurn\\\", message: \\\"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\\\n\\\\n{message}\\\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\\n   - delivery: {mode: \\\"announce\\\", channel: \\\"{channel}\\\", accountId: \\\"{accountId}\\\", to: \\\"{to}\\\"}\\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\\n\\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。\",\"timeoutSeconds\":60}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1063,"output":635,"cacheRead":48128,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":260,"totalTokens":49826,"cost":{"input":0.00014882,"output":0.0001778,"cacheRead":0.001347584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016742039999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780555922834,"responseId":"8cf15752-8571-40d8-95a8-c3ed5cf51c8b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b7d50ee","parentId":"7b5f11cb","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:52:10.496Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_E910vLuJkHRnfLIuvEa82267","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"dab72463-f2bc-4cfa-a3ed-762a98d5989f\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"faye-outbox-sender\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1780555929805,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780555929805,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"*/15 * * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\\n\\n对每个文件，执行：\\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\\n   - agentId: father\\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\\n   - schedule: {kind: \\\"at\\\", at: \\\"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\\\"}\\n   - payload: {kind: \\\"agentTurn\\\", message: \\\"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\\\n\\\\n{message}\\\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\\n   - delivery: {mode: \\\"announce\\\", channel: \\\"{channel}\\\", accountId: \\\"{accountId}\\\", to: \\\"{to}\\\"}\\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\\n\\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 60\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"none\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780556400000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"dab72463-f2bc-4cfa-a3ed-762a98d5989f","agentId":"father","name":"faye-outbox-sender","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780555929805,"updatedAtMs":1780555929805,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"*/15 * * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\n\n对每个文件，执行：\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\n   - agentId: father\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\n   - schedule: {kind: \"at\", at: \"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\"}\n   - payload: {kind: \"agentTurn\", message: \"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\n\\n{message}\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\n   - delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"{channel}\", accountId: \"{accountId}\", to: \"{to}\"}\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\n\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。","timeoutSeconds":60},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780556400000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780555930491}}
{"type":"message","id":"14ffd7e4","parentId":"1b7d50ee","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:52:14.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Both crons are set up. Now let me also mark urge-20260603-002 as delivered since it was already sent (though leaked), and update pending_urges.md.\n\nAlso, I should check if the pending-urges cron still has the stale lock issue. The lock from the last error should be gone now (it was from 12:04 today, and the process holding it timed out). Let me also clean up the stale lock file I found earlier.\n\nActually, the pending-urges cron runs every 6 hours with stagger, so the next run might be soon. Let me check the nextRunAtMs.\n\nnextRunAtMs: 1780567395301. Let me convert.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kCX9wFQiQubDLwF9l1cB3366","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"date -d @$((1780567395301/1000)) '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z' && echo \"---现在---\" && date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z'"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"date -d @$((1780567395301/1000)) '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z' && echo \\\"---现在---\\\" && date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z'\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":491,"output":247,"cacheRead":49792,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":149,"totalTokens":50530,"cost":{"input":0.00006874000000000001,"output":0.00006916000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001394176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001532076}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780555930544,"responseId":"8091358f-82d1-40b2-ba6f-11fedd841cc0"}}
