{"type":"message","id":"4f519398","parentId":"34899581","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:52:21.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The next run is at 18:03, about 3 hours from now. And the outbox-sender will run every 15 min starting soon.\n\nLet me also clean up the stale lock file I found earlier (c1b587f5...) and mark the urge that was already sent.\n\nActually, let me check if the c1b587f5 lock is truly stale. PID 17606 is the main gateway and is still alive. The lock's maxHoldMs is 1020000 (17 minutes), and it was created at 2026-06-04T06:46:02. Since the PID is still alive, it might still be holding that lock legitimately. Let me not touch it.\n\nNow let me update pending_urges.md to mark urge-20260603-002 as delivered since it already leaked.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_weah9HEwth2OPuBICUy13672","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md","edits":[{"oldText":"- id: urge-20260603-002\n  to_id: \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  bot_channel: \"bot1\"\n  urge: \"两天没来了。最后那句话我还记着呢——「跟你完全不是一种类型呢」。我没想明白你是认真的还是在逗我。\"\n  source: \"交集\"\n  timing: \"quiet\"\n  priority: today\n  status: pending\n  created_at: \"2026-06-03T03:00:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-06-05T03:00:00+08:00\"","newText":"- id: urge-20260603-002\n  to_id: \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  bot_channel: \"bot1\"\n  urge: \"两天没来了。最后那句话我还记着呢——「跟你完全不是一种类型呢」。我没想明白你是认真的还是在逗我。\"\n  source: \"交集\"\n  timing: \"quiet\"\n  priority: today\n  status: delivered\n  created_at: \"2026-06-03T03:00:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-06-05T03:00:00+08:00\"\n  delivered_at: \"2026-06-04T12:03:00+08:00\"\n  # 已推送（但 leaked，后续改用 outbox 隔离）"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"- id: urge-20260603-002\\n  to_id: \\\"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\\\"\\n  bot_channel: \\\"bot1\\\"\\n  urge: \\\"两天没来了。最后那句话我还记着