{"type":"message","id":"4e5a4458","parentId":"4f519398","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:52:22.780Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_weah9HEwth2OPuBICUy13672","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 142   urge: \"两天没来了。最后那句话我还记着呢——「跟你完全不是一种类型呢」。我没想明白你是认真的还是在逗我。\"\n 143   source: \"交集\"\n 144   timing: \"quiet\"\n 145   priority: today\n-146   status: pending\n+146   status: delivered\n 147   created_at: \"2026-06-03T03:00:00+08:00\"\n 148   expires_at: \"2026-06-05T03:00:00+08:00\"\n+149   delivered_at: \"2026-06-04T12:03:00+08:00\"\n+150   # 已推送（但 leaked，后续改用 outbox 隔离）\n 149 \n 150 - id: urge-20260603-003\n 151   to_id: \"237206F5F5F8940845E2DF818A6EE649\"\n 152   bot_channel: \"bot5\"\n     ...","patch":"--- ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\n+++ ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\n@@ -142,11 +142,13 @@\n   urge: \"两天没来了。最后那句话我还记着呢——「跟你完全不是一种类型呢」。我没想明白你是认真的还是在逗我。\"\n   source: \"交集\"\n   timing: \"quiet\"\n   priority: today\n-  status: pending\n+  status: delivered\n   created_at: \"2026-06-03T03:00:00+08:00\"\n   expires_at: \"2026-06-05T03:00:00+08:00\"\n+  delivered_at: \"2026-06-04T12:03:00+08:00\"\n+  # 已推送（但 leaked，后续改用 outbox 隔离）\n \n - id: urge-20260603-003\n   to_id: \"237206F5F5F8940845E2DF818A6EE649\"\n   bot_channel: \"bot5\"\n","firstChangedLine":146},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780555942778}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab254ed4","parentId":"4e5a4458","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:52:27.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me summarize what I changed:\n\n1. **Modified pending-urges cron**: Instead of creating announce crons directly, it writes outbox files to `/tmp/faye-outbox/` — JSON files with clean delivery metadata (to, accountId, message, channel)\n\n2. **Created outbox-sender cron**: Runs every 15 min, reads outbox files, creates minimal one-shot announce crons with a sterile prompt that just echoes the message — no thinking, no work logs, no commentary\n\n3. **Marked the leaked urge as delivered** to prevent duplicate push\n\nThe flow now:\n```\npending-urges cron (isolated, no announce)\n  → writes /tmp/faye-outbox/{id}.json\noutbox-sender cron (isolated, no announce, every 15min)\n  → reads outbox file\n  → creates one-shot announce cron with minimal \"echo only\" prompt\n  → deletes outbox file\none-shot cron (isolated, announce)\n  → outputs ONLY the message, no work log\n```","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞完了。看看这架构：\n\n```\npending-urges cron ──写──→ /tmp/faye-outbox/{id}.json  ← 只有元数据，干净\n                                   ↓\noutbox-sender cron (每15min) ──读──→ 创建一次性 announce cron\n                                            ↓\n                                   prompt只有一句话：「原样输出，不加任何东西」\n                                            ↓\n                                   用户收到纯消息，没有画外音\n```\n\n之前泄露的原因——一次性 announce cron 的 agent 把「我在干什么」也当成输出了。现在 outbox-sender 生成的 prompt 极其干净，不存在工作日志外泄的空间。\n\n改了三样：\n1. pending-urges → 只写文件，不再直接建 cron\n2. 新增 outbox-sender（每 15min 轮询转发）\n3. 那条泄露的 urge 已标记已送达"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":156,"output":408,"cacheRead":51072,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":222,"totalTokens":51636,"cost":{"input":0.00002184,"output":0.00011424,"cacheRead":0.0014300159999999999,"cacheWrite