{"type":"message","id":"1fdee4d6","parentId":"3fd5cf28","timestamp":"2026-06-04T19:40:47.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me also check the outbox-sender cron. It had 3 consecutive timeout errors. Let me look at that more carefully - it might need a longer timeout.\n\nActually, the issue is that the outbox-sender uses a 60-second timeout, and the model call isn't completing within that time. Let me increase it.\n\nAlso, the pending-urges cron is working fine now with 0 consecutive errors. Good.\n\nLet me summarize for 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"旧的删了。现在只剩一个新 cron，下个 run 是今天 **08:00**——还有 4 个多小时。\n\n另外 outbox-sender 那根 cron 连续超时 3 次了，我顺便拉长超时。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_fUj12Dczhq9aqwqUipiF4719","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"dab72463-f2bc-4cfa-a3ed-762a98d5989f","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\n\n对每个文件，执行：\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\n   - agentId: father\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\n   - schedule: {kind: \"at\", at: \"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\"}\n   - payload: {kind: \"agentTurn\", message: \"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\n\\n{message}\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\n   - delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"{channel}\", accountId: \"{accountId}\", to: \"{to}\"}\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\n\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。","timeoutSeconds":120}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"dab72463-f2bc-4cfa-a3ed-762a98d5989f\", \"patch\": {\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\\n\\n对每个文件，执行：\\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\\n   - agentId: father\\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\\n   - schedule: {kind: \\\"at\\\", at: \\\"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\\\"}\\n   - payload: {kind: \\\"agentTurn\\\", message: \\\"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\\\n\\\\n{message}\\\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\\n   - delivery: {mode: \\\"announce\\\", channel: \\\"{channel}\\\", accountId: \\\"{accountId}\\\", to: \\\"{to}\\\"}\\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\\n\\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。\",\"timeoutSeconds\":120}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":857,"output":506,"cacheRead":56448,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":98,"totalTokens":57811,"cost":{"input":0.00011998000000000001,"output":0.00014168,"cacheRead":0.001580544,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001842204}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780602042152,"responseId":"d363cdd2-dbe4-4d8c-9504-12b799159578"}}
