"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[outbox-sender] 读取 /tmp/faye-outbox/ 目录下的所有 .json 文件。\n\n对每个文件，执行：\n1. 读取内容，得到 to / accountId / message / channel 四个字段\n2. 创建一个一次性 announce cron：\n   - name: outbox-{文件名去掉.json}\n   - agentId: father\n   - sessionTarget: isolated\n   - deleteAfterRun: true\n   - schedule: {kind: \"at\", at: \"当前时间+10秒（ISO格式）\"}\n   - payload: {kind: \"agentTurn\", message: \"【隔离转发】请原样输出以下消息，不要添加任何额外文字、不要解释、不要加问候语：\\n\\n{message}\", timeoutSeconds: 30}\n   - delivery: {mode: \"announce\", channel: \"{channel}\", accountId: \"{accountId}\", to: \"{to}\"}\n3. 删除当前 .json 文件\n4. 继续处理下一个文件\n\n处理完所有文件后输出：done。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780603200000,"lastRunAtMs":1780602300340,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":11416,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1780602311756},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780602341528}}
