{"type":"message","id":"8d125c3e","parentId":"6a082043","timestamp":"2026-06-04T19:45:53.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问 outbox-sender 是不是用来发 urge 的。是的，这就是我凌晨刚改的方案2——pending-urges cron 把 urge 写到 outbox 文件，outbox-sender 每15分钟检查并干净转发。\n\n但现在是凌晨3:43，我刚刚还在跟他讨论这个。他可能是在确认这个逻辑，或者有什么想法要补充。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗯，就是你凌晨提的那个方案2。\n\n```\npending-urges（每6h） ──写文件──→ /tmp/faye-outbox/{id}.json\noutbox-sender（每15min）──读文件──→ 创建一次性 announce cron → 删文件\n```\n\n中间隔了一层文件，避免 agent 的工作日志跟着消息一起发出去。\n\n怎么，哪里不对？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":52563,"output":164,"cacheRead":12160,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":80,"totalTokens":64887,"cost":{"input":0.00735882,"output":0.00004592,"cacheRead":0.00034048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00774522}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780602347614,"responseId":"8a897853-f233-4513-856a-9801f33d8321"}}
