{"type":"message","id":"fee84972","parentId":"c45120c8","timestamp":"2026-06-04T19:46:43.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑问的是 outbox-sender cron 每15分钟检查一次 outbox 目录，这个查询消耗 Token 吗？\n\n我理解他是在问：outbox-sender 每次跑都要调一次模型（DeepSeek/LLM），即使 outbox 目录是空的，它的 prompt 本身就会消耗 Token——包括 input prompt 的 token 和可能的 output token。\n\n空跑时：\n- input: 整个 prompt（几百 token）\n- output: agent 读完文件发现没有，输出类似 \"done\" 之类的话（少量 token）\n\n所以即使空目录，每次 run 也要消耗 token 的 input 部分。\n\n他可能是想说这个频率太高了，有点浪费。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"消耗。每15分钟调一次模型，就算 outbox 空的，prompt 本身也吃 token——input 几百 tok，output 再吐个 \"无文件，跳过\" 之类的。\n\n要不要我改成长间隔？比如每 1 小时或者只在 pending-urges 跑完后延迟几分钟触发一次。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":12121,"output":213,"cacheRead":52608,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":144,"totalTokens":64942,"cost":{"input":0.00169694,"output":0.000059640000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0014730239999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032296039999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780602399587,"responseId":"0325fed6-3564-4cd6-9b00-e6d28c32049c"}}
